sources.title: Mars Needs Women (Sci-Fi, 1968) Tommy Kirk, Yvonne Craig | Movie
sources.description:
They Were Looking For Women. . . To Go All The Way!
Dop leads his fellow Martians to Earth on an interplanetary quest for females. Dop proves that Martians have impeccable taste when one of his first conquests turns out to be sexy scientist Dr. Marjorie Bolen. 

Original title: Mars Needs Women (1968) 

With multiple subtitle languages

Director & Writer: Larry Buchanan
Stars: Tommy Kirk, Yvonne Craig, Byron Lord 
Genres: Classics, Cult, Sci-Fi
Budget: $20,000 approximately 

00:00 Full Movie
03:40  Mysterious signals from Mars are decoded, revealing that Mars needs women for a mission.
11:07  The Martians demand the abandonment of the mission and threaten to leave without cooperation.
23:02  A group of individuals discuss their roles in Operation Frozen Sleep and their mission on Earth.
36:19  Mr. Fast is hypnotized and sent back to Seattle
46:58  The interview with Dr. Bolen discusses the possibility of Aliens from Mars and their impact on Earth.
53:52  Mars is the only planet where the possibility of life exists, with controversial canals believed to be an irrigation system
1:07:27  Experts confirm the disappearance of three women in less than 12 hours, suspecting Martians and identifying a potential target for a secret raid.
1:14:21  The theories and discoveries of Dr. Gustave Bolens, a renowned genetic expert, are exhibited in museums across the country.
